headline.main: CHINA IS JUBILANT AS CHIANG RETURNS; Attitude Shows Acceptance of Global War Strategy of Other Leaders

lead_paragraph: CHUNGKING, China, Dec. 2 (AP) -- China, welcoming Generalissimo Chiang Kai-shek home from Cairo, rejoiced today over the three-power pledge to crush Japan and restore all Chinese territory lost in half a century of struggle with the Japanese.
abstract: Gen and Mrs. Chiang Kai-shek return to Chungking
